name: Social Climber
description: The phenomenon of bragging about something you shouldn't be proud of, lying about accomplishments, or exaggerating the truth, in order to gain praise and recognition. People who show off their wealth is a sad and worrying phenomenon that can have a psychological impact on society. "(They) are less sensitive to social situations where their ego is definitely prioritized compared to social problems that are very concerning around them. Especially in the midst of the current Covid-19 pandemic, whose impact is not only giving a heavy blow to the health system, but also social life. The high economic disparity in society still triggers various social problems between the rich and the poor, so the current phenomenon of showing off wealth can trigger a psychological impact on society.
